The paper discusses deep learning and neuro-symbolic approaches, which are commonly studied in the sub-fields of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), and neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also introduces a new class of loss functions, which falls under the category of optimization and control (cs.LO).
